The sky, mountains, and high places such as the tops of very tall trees
are the favorite home of the Sylphs. Members of the Faerie race, the
Sylph are roughly human in appearance with the exception of the fully
functional wings on their backs. The Sylph are a culture that tends
towards goodness and lawfulness, but also one known for being able to
hold their own when it comes to the hearty consumption of the strong
libations served at the various festivals they hold. The Sylph are an
attractive race with looks to match their mental powers and quickness,
though they tend to be weaker and less robust than other races.
